tricks.name: Ollie
tricks.description: A fundamental skateboarding trick where the rider leaps into the air with the board.

tricks.name: Kickflip
tricks.description: A trick where the rider flips the board 360 degrees along the axis that extends from the nose to the tail.

tricks.name: Heelflip
tricks.description: Similar to the kickflip, but the rider uses their heel to flip the board.
